          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Readers who love Theif-ish plot</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10517119-pang?shelf=alpha-anti-hero">alpha-anti-hero</a>, 
