        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer26721177" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1142127830838489797">For what it is, it&apos;s brilliant. I read this book AGES ago, sometime in my teens. It was the first, and the best, of any Sidney Sheldon books I ever read. And though it is not a literary masterpiece, it is great. Revenge, heists, drama, romance, thrills...I still think it would be a box office hit if it was ever made into a Hollywood movie!<br/>If you want a light, entertaining, read that will keep you on the edge of your seat and take you back to the 80&apos;s, this is your book. Perfect vacation reading!</span>
  <span id="freeText1142127830838489797" style="display:none">For what it is, it's brilliant. I read this book AGES ago, sometime in my teens. It was the first, and the best, of any Sidney Sheldon books I ever read. And though it is not a literary masterpiece, it is great. Revenge, heists, drama, romance, thrills...I still think it would be a box office hit if it was ever made into a Hollywood movie!<br />If you want a light, entertaining, read that will keep you on the edge of your seat and take you back to the 80's, this is your book. Perfect vacation reading!</span>
